  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1604991576750-J0D5J3X8HC0JQWXVRK1U/10a-.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Week 9 and I am maintaining my clean (for me) desk and of course still digging everything about  Project Life.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1604991597034-S4MESUTXY8U0QP8U14OH/10b-dsc_0951.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>The hello sign by the door is by <a href=\"http://www.etsy.com/shop/sayhelloshop?ref=seller_info\">this etsy shop</a> and was purchased after seeing it in one of <a href=\"http://jlsdesignspot.blogspot.com/\">Jen's</a> instagrams. On the other side of the door is a rubber dog butt and tail that holds the leashes.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1604991622305-22E37CUMSREID4HUO59P/10c-dsc_09441.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I included a label from my favorite chips. They are crunchy and salted to perfection. JC thinks I like them because of the hint of soy sauce and lime, which is incredibly likely. We get them from Whole Foods, but it looks like <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B000LKZ0R2/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=wwwamytangeri-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B000LKZ0R2\">Amazon has a 24 pack</a>. Considering I can eat an entire bag in one sitting, I just might place an order.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"10d-dsc_09451.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1604991654986-UH00W86R70174Y7ZUAH4/10d-dsc_09451.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"10e-dsc_0946.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1604991654933-5DYMAHPKV9BS6KMIECTV/10e-dsc_0946.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"10f-dsc_0948.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1604991656142-E4C3JTT0R9I2WLBC8LMB/10f-dsc_0948.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Supplies: <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/_hambly%2520washi_/tapes/\">Hambly washi tape</a>, Studio Calico stamps, <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/pebbles/121402-welcome-christmas-abc-stamps/%3Ffilters%3D_pebbles%2Bstamps_\">Pebbles alphabet stamps</a>, <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/121136-amy-tangerine-goodness-slate-printed-chip-thickers-stickers/%3Ffilters%3D_amy%2Btangerine%2Bgoodness_\">Goodness Thickers</a>, <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/_october%2520afternoon%2520mini%2520market_/stickers/\">October Afternoon mini market stickers</a>.</p><p>It was a week full of work, work projects, hanging out with kids I see often and people I only see occasionally. It was a week of eating well but not exercising enough. Although if you count scraping snow and ice off my rental car in Utah, then I got a decent work out in. As much as I love Yogurtland, Farr's Fresh may actually be even better. They had a salted caramel that was to die for and they have one of my favorites ever - Dole pineapple whip.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1604991675670-QMFTVY96PO64FQFNY2NV/10g-farrs1.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>One of JC's friends from high school was in town starring in Albert Herring, so we went to the Opera for the first time together. I think the last time I went was on a field trip in grade school (while living in Chicago). We got a great deal on tickets, considering our seats usually go for $150+ each. It was enjoyable, and although it was in English, the subtitles on the screen helped big time.</p><p>Thanks for looking! You can see all my Project Life posts <a href=\"http://static.squarespace.com/static/54763a73e4b0d25603e00ba7/54a756aae4b0f2d6f3befd4e/54a773bfe4b0f2d6f3c1cc6d/1420260287567/project-life?format=original\">here</a>.</p>"
}